{
  "stem": "21308.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there on every concrete post with the porcelain insulators for the electrified fence and on each post there was a sign and it was a yellow sign with salmon-colored letters on it which read, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know what that means in English?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Entry strongly forbidden, state secret police, Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's-- I reckon that that would be the first time when you could link it all together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew that gassing went on, but we'd only just learned about it, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- after we crossed the Rhine-- we crossed the Rhine on the 23rd of March, '45-- we overran a farm and I found a vehicle backed into a wagon shed and I thought it was a mobile bath unit, the sort of thing you'd be useful to have.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said one of my chaps who was fluent in German, do you know, that looks like a mobile bathroom to me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, we could do with that, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went and had look at it and he said, that's not a-- that's-- that's a gas wagon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it still had in the box containers, I think it called itself Zyklon gas-- Zyklon B, I think it was called.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when we looked in the back and saw the filthy mess, there was-- there was no doubt about it what it had been used for, and it wasn't cattle that had been going.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was after we crossed the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We crossed the Rhine, as I told you, 23rd, 24th, 25th, 26th of March.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was between the very end of March and the first days in April we saw this lorry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wrote that up in my-- my reminiscences.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, you have to remember we were soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
